Class DefaultAddressAutocompletePlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.address.DefaultAddressAutocompletePlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAddressAutocompletePlugin

    public class DefaultAddressAutocompletePlugin
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAddressAutocompletePlugin
    Default plugin for Address auto complete/auto fill. Provides functionality equivalent to version 7 AddressAutocompleteUtil class.
